      "content": "but even when i try to be better, i just mess it up. it's like i'm constanty failing them. sometimes i look at them sleeping and i just think... if i wasn't around, everything would be so much easier for them. they wouldn't have to deal with my stuff anymore. they could just be happy without me constantly dragging them into my chaos.",
